{"tid":273294,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"配左副兩週con 想請教下巴絲","createTime":"2017-06-06T12:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T04:47:34.000Z","uid":17065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c496521e8014dfe6404ddf80340ea92178e1ccd","tid":273294,"uid":17065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T12:25:14.000Z","msg":"一日用完之後 係咪要浸殺菌水？<br />\n有邊隻好推介 唔會傷眼<br />\n拎出來用果陣係咪要搵鹽水捽佢？<br />\n軟con都要？ 同埋鹽水你地係買定自己開？<br />\n眼藥水邊隻無 防腐又唔會la眼？<br />\n暫時諗到係咁多 唔該巴絲指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c370df8f55c825aa45687e6e85125fec850c6e8f","tid":273294,"uid":97482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T12:49:28.000Z","msg":"配個陣啲職員冇教你架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用洗con水就得啦"},{"pid":"df17fc895da04b185e3562f5ef61652b96893a54","tid":273294,"uid":17065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T13:25:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>配個陣啲職員冇教你架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用洗con水就得啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係韓國買 果陣唔記得左問<br />\n洗con水 係浸住 一日換一次？<br />\n定係可以拎來捽埋"},{"pid":"dbae842138d8d28a609b20995636ce235eb73f3e","tid":273294,"uid":93269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T13:33:22.000Z","msg":"1. 鏡片放手心加con 水，捽下鏡片兩面 <br />\n2. 用新con水沖乾淨<br />\n3. 用新con水浸8小時<br />\n<br />\n以我經驗，軟同硬con 都要咁做。唔好慳con 水"},{"pid":"b8a78c42e2267ad260849247d2f002abfeb854aa","tid":273294,"uid":53173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:15:52.000Z","msg":"自己開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想盲？"},{"pid":"ceb580d301c58782de7ec2e5d543b282ef68f9a3","tid":273294,"uid":17065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,